1. You may use any programming language you are comfortable with to write a program that encrypts and decrypts a file on demand.
2. Feel free to use any libraries available online. You are not required to implement the cryptographic algorithms from scratch. Any cryptosystem is acceptable (e.g., AES, RSA, ECC, etc.).
3. You may choose whichever programming language you find most convenient.
Additional features may earn up to 10 bonus points. 

